  17:				;	|  WRTTRK CODE  |	VARIABLE LENGTH HALT/NMI/OUTI ROUTINE
  18:				;	|		|
  19:				;	|---------------|  +N
  20:				;	|		|
  21:				;	|  TRACK IMAGE  |	POINTED TO BY 'TRKPTR'
